"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acd131980852b3d4e332cf8474c2fd7c7642148","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9442a808c97205f3222b830f6788cf995cd197","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"887f2fc5f10da0a2a4729336971705a483a6fbbb","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:51:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">補充多少少：真假withdraw個個理據其實係好薄弱，我地要出師有名，將重點放係其餘4點</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:52:13.000Z","msg":"運動成功重點係出師有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位謹記"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:53:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出師有名放核彈個個都拍手<br />\n出師無名做英雄都比人鬧</span></span>"},{"pid":"6e9c78e63eedc890894c46dddd275a6cbb711b86","tid":1542574,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n唔好再講假withdraw"},{"pid":"0c2eb102ceb757fa5043f5366873cecc6fc0e5b0","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"推爆佢，唔好比人帶風向"},{"pid":"df5f9b020871d3cfefc10e8482d451d934f5f9f6","tid":1542574,"uid":9049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c03a846f2960b8b0311998c6c7f7ba35d36f0376","tid":1542574,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:49:51.000Z","msg":"同意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:54:13.000Z","msg":"各地區連儂牆要人，文宣大量要大解釋清楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.05"},{"pid":"f92b216d561a2ea3cb2599c30a2ffa18f3d1af5e","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續推，等美國可以出手做野，要開始打底啦<br />\n如果你keep住講假withdraw,到時星期日佢宣佈撤回，依招你點拆？到時咪又要loop番仲有四個，咁不如依加開始做文宣，仲有幾日時間<br />\n要做到五大訴求or美國制裁<br />\n掉番個波比林鄭<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"24b5306a7a62624f1dc798b1175b4b726f1fc712","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ec61ccedda08af081fbed5b67d5c11cdc31e91f","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13c406b7034204f4af52500870230d3e83f0b7ad","tid":1542574,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d4dd053f42c1ea3115eeb20cf4807a9df7ea13d","tid":1542574,"uid":86863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"方向正確"},{"pid":"0c088bac96ebb30621839dac1486fc95e2c0f165","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e81c4eb78381e60a127be6048d83dee6f039ea08","tid":1542574,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88b59cdf35183e7561459b8181c21badefe28dcd","tid":1542574,"uid":155497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh"},{"pid":"98be10555